snippet.title: Ultra Mega Cats - Official Kagero Character Trailer | The MIX Fall Showcase 2024
snippet.description: Meet Kagero and see this Ninja Assassin damage dealer in action in this new trailer for Ultra Mega Cats. Blast your way through hordes of enemies in Ultra Mega Cats, a cooperative roguelike third-person shooter. Play As one of the Mega Cats, armed to the fangs with a wide variety of abilities and escape captivity from your Rodent and Bird Overlords! Ultra Mega Cats will be available on PC.
